a rocketry scientist convicted of 
trying to ship sophisticated us missile technology to egypt has 
been sentenced to 46 months in prison 
abdelkader helmy 41 also was fined 358690 and ordered to 
forfeit about a halfmillion dollars all part of what prosecutors 
said were 1 million in payments dispensed to helmy by egyptian 
intelligence operatives via swiss banks 
this is not a cloakanddagger espionage case us district 
