lithuanias parliament wednesday fell nine votes 
short of changing the republics constitution to legalize multiple 
political parties the first threat to the communist partys 
constitutionally guaranteed supremacy in the soviet union 
the 2191 vote was shy of the 228 needed for the twothirds 
