here is a history of jobcutting programs at 
international business machines corp since 1986 
september 1986 ibm announces retirement incentives that add 
five years to the age and five years to the length of service of 
eligible employees for purposes of calculating retirement benefits 
by the end of 1987 15000 employees accept the incentives 
including 13000 in the united states 
june 1988 ibm announces separation incentives aimed at 
